prompts.title: Close-Up Detail
prompts.description: Tight frame with shallow depth of field and texture emphasis
prompts.prompt: A tight frame isolates a calligrapher's pen tip kissing paper. Shallow depth of field blurs the studio into soft haze while the focus plane reveals fibers of the paper and ink texture. Tiny hand tremors animate the moment.
searchTerms: tight frame with shallow depth of field and texture emphasis

prompts.title: Dramatic Backlight
prompts.description: Dim hangar with strong rim lighting and atmospheric beams
prompts.prompt: Inside a dim hangar, a lone figure steps forward as a dominant rear key carves a bright rim around their silhouette. Ambient is tightly controlled; thin haze reveals defined beams that stretch across the floor. The subject pauses in near-silhouette, breathing visible in the light, with restrained flare glinting along the edge of the frame.
searchTerms: dim hangar with strong rim lighting and atmospheric beams

prompts.title: Low Angle
prompts.description: Great for heroic shots and emphasizing power. The low angle creates dramatic perspective and makes subjects appear more imposing.
prompts.prompt: At the base of a modern tower, the camera tilts up from below the horizon, exaggerating verticals. The subject stands near the facade, appearing larger-than-life as clouds sweep past the building's soaring edges.
searchTerms: great for heroic shots and emphasizing power. the low angle creates dramatic perspective and makes subjects appear more imposing.

prompts.title: Natural Sunlight
prompts.description: Great for outdoor documentary and natural scenes. The realistic lighting approach avoids artificial enhancement for authentic feel.
prompts.prompt: On a cliffside trail, a hiker pauses under clear skies. A directional solar key casts defined penumbra across rocky ground as sky dome bounce gently lifts shadows. White balance stays neutral and contrast feels realistic with no artificial fill—just sun, wind, and ocean spray.
searchTerms: great for outdoor documentary and natural scenes. the realistic lighting approach avoids artificial enhancement for authentic feel.

prompts.title: Neon City Night
prompts.description: Rain-slicked alley with neon signage and atmospheric bloom
prompts.prompt: A rain-slicked alley glows with saturated cyan‑magenta signage. Localized colored pools light passing pedestrians while subtle atmospheric bloom softens bright edges. Mixed CCT storefronts flicker as crisp specular micro-contrast sparks on wet asphalt and chrome scooter mirrors.

prompts.title: Soft Golden Hour
prompts.description: Coastal overlook at golden hour with warm lighting and nostalgic atmosphere
prompts.prompt: A quiet coastal overlook at golden hour. Low-angle warm sunlight paints a couple leaning on a railing as elongated soft-edged shadows trail behind them. Warm rim separation outlines their faces with a honeyed glow, gentle falloff keeps contrast soft, and slightly lifted blacks give a nostalgic warmth. White balance sits around ~4500K as they trade calm smiles and watch waves roll in.

prompts.title: Wide Valley Shot
prompts.description: Broad valley view with layered depth and scale
prompts.prompt: From a ridge at dawn, the camera holds a broad field of view over a valley. A small lone hiker occupies minimal frame space while layered foreground rocks, sweeping midground meadows, and distant mountains establish grand scale and depth.
searchTerms: broad valley view with layered depth and scale
